1
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,520
Dailing.

2
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:02,280
You are not dead.

3
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,380
Father.

4
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,860
Kneel down.

5
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,560
Do you know what you did wrong?

6
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,080
No.

7
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,280
I went through hell

8
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:51,039
and high water with my brothers to build this empire.

9
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,039
If you touch them,

10
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,680
you're shaking the foundation of Sihai Group,

11
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,520
and chilling the hearts of those old brothers.

12
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,740
I'm clearing the parasites in Sihai.

13
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,000
I'm helping you.

14
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:02,960
Helping me?

15
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,330
You did it in public.

16
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,140
When the news spreads,

17
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,280
people on the street will

18
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,440
know about the internal strife in Sihai Group.

19
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,500
Siam Group and other groups will take advantage of this

20
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,940
and muddy the waters completely.

21
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,560
Using violence is not a skill.

22
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,680
It's stupidity.

23
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:29,160
I didn't handle it cleanly this time.

24
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,360
You're my only son.

25
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,400
Everything I have

26
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,480
is yours.

27
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,480
Biyang died in Tangong.

28
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,200
About this matter,

29
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,530
what are you going to do?

30
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,820
Rest assured, Father.

31
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,050
I'll give Mrs. Biyang an explanation.

32
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,600
Get up.

33
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,360
Go back.

34
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,320
If we're going to do this,

35
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,520
we have to do it clean.

36
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,840
Wipe them out completely.

37
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,780
You're more ruthless than I thought.

38
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:13,840
Got it.

39
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,600
Angwei.

40
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,520
Angwei.

41
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,930
You'll be mine sooner or later.

42
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,880
Madam.

43
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:43,960
Master.

44
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,690
Angwei is young and promising,

45
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,040
and can be considered your capable assistant.

46
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:53,160
In the future, when you hand over the entire Sihai Group to him,

47
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,360
you can rest assured.

48
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,320
However,

49
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,080
last night,

50
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,690
he brought a woman back.

51
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,920
I can manage how he deals with the veterans,

52
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,180
but can I control him playing with women?

53
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:08,920
As for you,

54
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,840
although you are his stepmother,

55
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,640
you must take on the responsibilities of a mother.

56
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,000
Yes, I understand, sir.

57
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,240
I will take good care of Awei.

58
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,440
I will make those

59
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,880
unpresentable women

60
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:26,240
give up their thoughts of clinging to our Chen family.

61
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,940
Did you find anything?

62
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,400
Young master.

63
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,840
Five years ago, everyone saw Dailing fall into the sea.

64
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,240
You searched frantically for her body.

65
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,600
You looked for a long time but couldn't find it.

66
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,120
In such deep water, there's no chance of survival.

67
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,200
Not finding a body

68
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,400
doesn't mean she is dead.

69
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,780
Go investigate that woman named Feifei.

70
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,720
Look into every detail.

71
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,690
Let's see if your sword skills have improved.

72
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,060
Remember this ruthlessness.

73
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,920
That's the only way to make Angwei

74
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,400
die a miserable death.

75
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,360
What?

76
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,780
Thinking about him again?

77
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,040
No.

78
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,040
Don't forget,

79
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:03,160
he pushed you off the boat with his own hands

80
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,360
and tried to kill you.

81
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:06,560
Such a heartless beast.

82
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,400
Why do you still care about him?

83
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,080
I hate him.

84
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,360
I was so stupid.

85
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,920
I thought he really loved me

86
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,400
and would protect me.

87
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,860
But what happened?

88
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,600
He watched my mother burn to death.

89
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:30,360
He even pushed me into the sea with his own hands.

90
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,600
He is a butcher.

91
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,320
This tattoo

92
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,700
was tattooed on me by him personally.

93
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,960
Even if it's just to grab a knife,

94
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,800
you shouldn't have sacrificed so much.

95
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,600
A beast like Angwei

96
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,490
is not worth risking your own life for.

97
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,690
As long as I can get revenge,

98
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,610
I don't care if it costs my life.

99
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,680
Biyang is dead.

100
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,720
Who should be next?

101
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,920
Lapeng,

102
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,560
Ruannila,

103
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,040
Danpa,

104
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,520
or who?

105
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,040
We must hold off our actions for now.

106
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,840
After the battle at Tangong,

107
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:49,440
Angwei is sending more people everywhere to investigate.

108
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,570
Although he hasn't suspected you yet,

109
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,440
because of your face,

110
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,010
he has started looking into it.

111
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,320
And there is Ruannila.

112
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,640
She always keeps an eye on the women around Angwei.

113
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:03,480
If we act rashly now,

114
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,240
she might catch us.

115
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,400
The loss outweighs the gain.

116
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:09,800
You're right.

117
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,440
Ruannila is a viper.

118
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,650
Once she bites, she doesn't let go.

119
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,880
But at least we confirmed one thing.

120
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:20,920
That is,

121
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,340
Angwei still has an obsession

122
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,320
with Dailing.

123
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,000
If that's the case,

124
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,000
why don't we use it to our advantage?

125
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,090
You keep staying by his side

126
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,240
to earn his trust.

127
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,760
This way,

128
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,890
he can become a real knife in our hands.

129
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,890
There is a good opportunity right now.

130
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:46,410
Tomorrow is the seventh day of Biyang's passing.

131
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,680
His wife

132
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,460
will host his funeral.

133
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:54,040
There will definitely be people fighting for the shipping routes at the funeral.

134
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,440
If I help him win the routes then,

135
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,660
infiltrating the Sihai Group

136
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,460
will be a matter of course.

137
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,880
Since this game

138
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,210
started with the shipping routes,

139
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,290
let's continue with the shipping routes.

140
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,400
What they owe me,

141
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,760
I will definitely

142
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,560
get it back.

143
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,130
Hurry up.

144
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,680
Young Master.

145
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,520
The killer of Biyang hasn't been found yet,

146
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,120
but his funeral is tomorrow.

147
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,440
We...

148
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,040
I know.

149
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,400
You may leave.

150
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,040
Miss Feifei has been found.

151
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,370
She is now at Tan Palace.

152
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,400
Prepare the car.

153
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,860
We're going to Tan Palace.

154
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:58,850
Where did you go?

155
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,000
I just took a day off.

156
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,780
Are you mad about that?

157
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:10,260
Why are you stricter than my boss?

158
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,520
But compared to my whereabouts,

159
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,520
I think you should be more concerned about Biyang.

160
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,160
His funeral is tomorrow.

161
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,120
You'll go, right?

162
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,160
It seems you care a lot about my whereabouts.

163
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:27,960
I'd rather

164
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,200
lend you a hand.

165
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,720
I got news that

166
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,400
for the funeral tomorrow,

167
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,660
Ou Shaowen has prepared a generous gift.

168
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,800
He not only wants to console Mrs. Biyang,

169
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,520
but also in the name of assisting the investigation

170
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:42,080
and stabilizing the situation,

171
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,440
to request Mrs. Biyang

172
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:46,800
to temporarily entrust the route to the Siam Group.

173
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,160
Does Miss Feifei think

174
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:52,690
that the men under my command are all useless,

175
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,480
and can't find out any news at all?

176
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,210
Finding out and getting it done

177
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,860
are two different things.

178
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,440
But if I said

179
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,040
I could make Mrs. Biyang

180
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,480
willingly

181
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,500
hand the route over to you,

182
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,960
would you believe me?

183
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:14,600
You?

184
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,080
Then let's make a bet.

185
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,800
If I can get Mrs. Biyang

186
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,130
to hand the route to you,

187
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,880
you must promise me something.

188
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:23,210
Not many people dare to make demands of me.

189
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,520
You are the first.

190
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,520
Then let's

191
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,040
bet on it.

192
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,200
Dailing.

193
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,650
Is it really you?

194
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:25,890
Come with me.

195
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,880
Ou Shaowen.
